data.title: Check Channel Guide and Call 855-507-5823
data.meta_description: View the DIRECTV channel guide and lineup, including HD channels by package. Want to switch to DIRECTV? Call 855-507-5823 today.
data.text:
Gemini™ device

Elevate your TV viewing experience with our new Gemini™ device. Easily access live TV and thousands of streaming apps like Netflix, Max, Prime Video and more, with just a click of a button.

**Req's paid separate subscription for Netflix, Max, Prime Video (see amazon.com/amazonprime for details) and other 3rd party apps. Restrictions apply. High speed internet-connected compatible device required. Google login required.

Get more popular channels than DISH™

Based on 2023 Nielsen ratings (top ten network channels excluding premiums) and comparing DIRECTV satellite base packages vs. DISH America’s Top 120.

Sign up and start watching instantly with the DIRECTV app^^ – even before your equipment is setup.

With DIRECTV On Demand, there’s always something to watch. With 65,000+ On Demand shows and movies at your fingertips, you can binge your favorite shows or put on a movie at any time, whether on a TV or connected device.*

^^Available only in the U.S. (excl. Peurto Rico and U.S.V.I.). Not all channels available to stream. Limited to up to 3 concurrent streams. Restr's apply. Visit directv.com/app for more information.

*Internet-connected Gemini device required. Actual number of shows and movies will vary based on programming package. Additional fees apply for new releases and certain library titles.

DIRECTV – leader in sports

DIRECTV is the leader in sports.‡ With more regional sports networks than DISH, there’s no competition2.

Want sports 24/7? We’ve got everything fans like you crave with the top sports networks plus national, regional, and local sports channels like ESPN, Golf Channel, and more.✝︎

‡Claim based on offering of Nat’l and Regional Sports Networks. RSNs avail. with CHOICE package or higher. Availability of RSNs varies by ZIP code and package.

2Compared to cable, Dish and most streaming providers. RSNs avail. with CHOICE package or higher. Availability of RSNs varies by ZIP code and package.​

✝︎✝︎Availability of channels varies based on package selection. Regional Sports Networks included in CHOICE Package or higher. Blackout restr’s apply. Avail. of RSNs varies by zip code and pkg.
